88
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:23,720
Xie Yi.

89
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,240
Let me do it.

90
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,720
Wait.

91
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:30,519
She...

92
