and Dai.

104
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,319
If you turn yourself in,
you'll get a lighter sentence.

105
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,800
Mr. Li.

106
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,560
If you think

107
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,759
