260
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:56,519
that Mr. Li Ze Liang

261
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:57,759
must be removed from the post
of chairman.

262
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,320
That's because a tainted chairman

263
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:06,279
with bad leadership

264
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,440
