to the company whatsoever."

265
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,639
Come on. Let's vote.

266
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:13,279
I second that.

267
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,960
Ms. Shi, please take a stand.

268
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,279
