621
00:27:46,519 --> 00:27:47,480
be bygones.

622
00:27:47,799 --> 00:27:48,440
That's right.

623
00:27:48,599 --> 00:27:49,799
We'll all be friends now.

624
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,240
