625
00:27:52,319 --> 00:27:52,680
Here.

626
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:55,279
Firstly,

627
00:27:55,319 --> 00:27:56,720
I want to express my deepest gratitude

628
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,599
