629
00:27:58,119 --> 00:28:00,039
After all, your vote

630
00:28:00,359 --> 00:28:02,119
is crucial to me.

631
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,359
Also,

632
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:05,599
