634
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,240
Are you really planning

635
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:11,119
to sell your stocks in Ocean?

636
00:28:12,079 --> 00:28:12,839
Of course.

637
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:15,079
