638
00:28:15,279 --> 00:28:16,480
left for me in Ocean.

639
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,920
After the transfer of the stocks,

640
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:19,559
I'll stop

641
00:28:19,839 --> 00:28:21,119
