662
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:49,680
Perfect. I'm going to.

663
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,319
Let's go together, Ms. Shi.

664
00:28:51,799 --> 00:28:52,200
Sure.

665
00:28:52,359 --> 00:28:52,799
Okay.

666
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,000
Be my guest.

667
00:28:55,559 --> 00:28:56,839
