Is Xie Ming Hao using her

688
00:29:53,359 --> 00:29:55,240
to threaten you?

689
00:29:57,319 --> 00:29:57,960
That's right.

690
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,839
Indeed, she's still alive.

691
00:30:02,559 --> 00:30:03,839
So Ze Liang is right.

692
00:30:04,599 --> 00:30:06,839
