by a galaxy.

779
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:52,880
Do you remember

780
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,640
the first time we met?

781
00:33:54,319 --> 00:33:55,119
Of course.

782
00:33:57,079 --> 00:33:58,200
It was snowing that day.

783
00:33:59,079 --> 00:34:00,559
