it won't be wrong.

832
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:24,639
Okay. I got it.

833
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,480
Thank you.

834
00:36:30,559 --> 00:36:31,119
Xie Yi.

835
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:32,519
